    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Yome Clan <br />Whether you're from the Hidden Sand Village or not, its in your clan's blood to survive barren wastes. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Constitution or Wisdom score by 1, to a max of 20.</li><li>With or without your Shizukugan active, you always know where to find the nearest source of water within a 1-mile radius of you.</li><li>You have advantage on checks and saving throws made to resist hot or dry weather conditions.</li></ul>",
